title: Support main looking for a team.
body:
Honestly I'm not high ranked. I know. I'm a support main and I want to be a part of a serious team. I can do my job and I can do it well. Free every night at around midnight and on Sundays and Mondays all day and night.
I have skype and can use that for chatting.

replies.body: hi mate looking for a serious player as a support main add me in game
That would be awesome. Sorry, I was on a holiday.
